{"tid":1059761,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"京都一日遊 行程","createTime":"2019-03-13T10:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T07:29:43.000Z","uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ad0ca752f259a82816892abfb326b64a032d03ac","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"黎緊會去京都一日遊 3月尾<br />\n大阪市出發 主要想去千本鳥居影下相<br />\n知道清水寺裝修緊所以未必會去<br />\n但去完千本鳥居 <br />\n京都有咩地方好去呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有諗過去嵐山竹林同小火車<br />\n但就好似一日太趕<br />\n求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ebcf5209be38f08d7954bbbc5116b4abb49598","tid":1059761,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"點會趕，呢度年中大把人都係咁 plan，人地咪又係一樣去得哂。"},{"pid":"594d47b51ca73e052e90e7e6f35201270dbc11dd","tid":1059761,"uid":225973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"幾到到幾點走？"},{"pid":"df5d970276c169f0b5cc293cae86dfd34bfc47bd","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:50:44.000Z","msg":"因為3月尾去就想著埋和服<br />\n咁應該去京都著定大阪城著<br />\n會有埋櫻花景"},{"pid":"807af2bf05c3e68bfc7e3eac0897c62fcebb9eae","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594d47b51ca73e052e90e7e6f35201270dbc11dd","tid":1059761,"uid":225973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"幾到到幾點走？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"預1100am到京都"},{"pid":"edf4c9cfc76f636b2f9e6512e9cb106fc6d17267","tid":1059761,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"伏見 加 宇治 啦"},{"pid":"0f461057faaa39ef6ba2003f2159d818fbe59a0b","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"和服 + 千本鳥居  <br />\n可以加多樣咩玩一日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7a590f8b37db4cfeb940f972a9714a106826b4","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f461057faaa39ef6ba2003f2159d818fbe59a0b","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"和服 + 千本鳥居  <br />\n可以加多樣咩玩一日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b37d3646d5d8c3a1cc72882629a481bbe7c536","tid":1059761,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b7a590f8b37db4cfeb940f972a9714a106826b4","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f461057faaa39ef6ba2003f2159d818fbe59a0b","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"和服 + 千本鳥居  <br />\n可以加多樣咩玩一日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:20:04.000Z","msg":"求建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"金閣寺啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"262ced431b2cde4cd2549a2c9e4b0bd5e0581bb8","tid":1059761,"uid":124241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"11點到, 要換和服(起碼搞成粒鐘) 花季勁多人排隊 , 12點幾先出發 , 又未食野, 即係至快都1點半開始行程。我就會伏見之後搭京鐵上清水或者八坂神社 ,  咁已經好趕<br />\nPS 清水門口仲有好多街同地方可以影"},{"pid":"ee8b847191b63e64e1b4cb0a5a2a1d6564db6eb7","tid":1059761,"uid":121068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"262ced431b2cde4cd2549a2c9e4b0bd5e0581bb8","tid":1059761,"uid":124241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"11點到, 要換和服(起碼搞成粒鐘) 花季勁多人排隊 , 12點幾先出發 , 又未食野, 即係至快都1點半開始行程。我就會伏見之後搭京鐵上清水或者八坂神社 ,  咁已經好趕<br />\nPS 清水門口仲有好多街同地方可以影"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T15:55:07.000Z","msg":"因為主要想去千本鳥居 <br />\n清水裝修應該唔會去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce61d651447d3f1c34ec5c5393323105b727776","tid":1059761,"uid":29791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"如果你要著和服嘅話，點解唔早少少過京都？<br />\n3月尾已經係入京都櫻花旺季，到時真係度度都爆多人<br />\n你真係要預返時間，唔係嘅話你等換和服都等死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633915e00f8ca660b3bda52a08629a473469a5ed","tid":1059761,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"朝早先伏見，後宇治，番四條一帶食個晏，再坐嵐電去嵐山小火車來回，然後坐巴士去埋金閣寺，入黑就落番京都河原町晚飯，最後去円山公園散步<br />\n其實仲有好多點可以去，不過見樓主好似唔想咁趕，唯有建議咁樣轉個圈算"},{"pid":"858328cb5fb0dd8487524fc34afaa35a0d454f9f","tid":1059761,"uid":71939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633915e00f8ca660b3bda52a08629a473469a5ed","tid":1059761,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"朝早先伏見，後宇治，番四條一帶食個晏，再坐嵐電去嵐山小火車來回，然後坐巴士去埋金閣寺，入黑就落番京都河原町晚飯，最後去円山公園散步<br />\n其實仲有好多點可以去，不過見樓主好似唔想咁趕，唯有建議咁樣轉個圈算"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T04:04:00.000Z","msg":"一日去到咁多地方？<br />\n<br />\n我想係京都玩一日<br />\n朝早：8阪神杜+円山公園+花見小路<br />\n下午：新京極商店街<br />\n<br />\n會唔會好快行完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd0d5fb9167f608efd29da3d98f717f16d589fb","tid":1059761,"uid":29791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"858328cb5fb0dd8487524fc34afaa35a0d454f9f","tid":1059761,"uid":71939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"633915e00f8ca660b3bda52a08629a473469a5ed","tid":1059761,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"朝早先伏見，後宇治，番四條一帶食個晏，再坐嵐電去嵐山小火車來回